```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Adult with metabolic syndrome<br/>considering intermittent fasting] --> EatDis{History of<br/>eating disorder?}
    EatDis -->|Yes| Excluded[EXCLUDED: do not initiate IF<br/>refer to eating-disorder care]
    EatDis -->|No| Adolescent{Adolescent?}
    Adolescent -->|Yes| Excluded
    Adolescent -->|No| Pregnant{Pregnant or<br/>breastfeeding?}
    Pregnant -->|Yes| Excluded
    Pregnant -->|No| BMI{BMI category?}

    BMI -->|BMI under 25| Marginal[MARGINAL: real-world benefit<br/>may be modest or absent<br/>counsel with caveats]
    BMI -->|BMI 25-29.9| Marginal
    BMI -->|BMI 30 or higher| Pharm{On insulin or<br/>sulfonylurea?}

    Pharm -->|Yes| AdjustMed[Adjust pharmacotherapy<br/>before initiating IF<br/>monitor for hypoglycemia]
    Pharm -->|No| CVD{Established CVD?}

    AdjustMed --> CVD
    CVD -->|Yes| Conservative[Use mild protocol only<br/>avoid eating windows under 8h<br/>per AHA 2024 subgroup signal [REF:7]]
    CVD -->|No| Suitable[SUITABLE: first-line lifestyle intervention<br/>Significant pooled benefits on FBS, HbA1c,<br/>HOMA-IR, LDL-C, IL-6, body weight, BP [REF:7]]

    Conservative --> Protocol[Recommended protocol:<br/>12:12 to 14:10 TRE]
    Suitable --> Protocol2[Recommended protocols:<br/>16:8 TRE first-line<br/>5:2 if motivated<br/>FMD if physician-supervised]
```
